          with a curated drink recommendation from the external database (TheCocktailDB.com).
          A user can then save cocktails to their own drink lists, create different categories/lists,
          and add their drinks to any and all of their personal drink lists. Create drink lists for any occasion and clink glasses with your friends - Bottoms Up!
